      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOLICIT (3) has a strong overall record having 21 wins and 28 places from 66 starts including a last start success (22.29) over 390m at Shepparton. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. Well placed here and can go close with a clear run. PAW XABIA (2) had been in great form but missed the frame latest when seventh (23.06) in a Free For All at Geelong. Generally safe to begin but was always well back last time. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Should be in this for a long way. MAX PEARL (1) won again in another strong performance after leading them home to make it back to back wins, scoring at Warrnambool over 390m (22.42). Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Sure to measure up. THORKILDSEN (7) is worth consideration.",
